title: Rusty GTR Surfboard
description:
The GT is your go-to board in average everyday surf. Back foot oriented surfers will enjoy the lift, drive and skate of this small wave machine. 

Deep single concave, a slight vee flaring off the corners, average entry rocker, curved rails, and flat tail rocker. Wider than average tail with volume shifted back. Ride 1-3" shorter than your shortboard.
